## Declares

### Primitive: Record

**Id**: `record`

**Name**: Record

**Kind**: Primitive

**Purpose:** Defines structured values with named attributes.

**ValueType:**

```ts
type PrimitiveRecordFieldValueType = PrimitiveScalar | PrimitiveStructure | ... WIP

type PrimitiveRecordField = {
  name: string;
  description: string;
  purpose: string;
  valueType: PrimitiveRecordFieldValueType;
};

type PrimitiveRecord = {
  [key: string]: PrimitiveRecordField;
};
```

**Value:**

```ts
type PrimitiveRecordValue = {
  values: Record<string, PrimitiveRecordFieldValueType>;
};
```

